  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the change score for the PedsQL short form Diabetes
      and Core Modules and the Patient Assessment of Chronic Illness Care measured at baseline
      (before changing care delivery models) and 12 months after transitioning to the team model of
      care delivery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Pediatric Type 1 Diabetes Mellitus patients and their parents will complete the forms before
      and 12 months after the diabetes clinic at Children's Mercy Hospital in Kansas City, MO
      transitions to a team model of care delivery.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
